                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/4e99f18b-e1bf-401c-95bc-ea856029e33f&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/4e99f18b-e1bf-401c-95bc-ea856029e33f&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_34h failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;New size wrong 10485760 != 1000
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/102975&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/102975&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-477.27.1.el8_8.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/102975&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/102975&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-477.27.1.el8_lustre.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;Please provide additional information about the failure here&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems the file size didn&apos;t change after doing ftruncate, this subtest so far only failed when set the base dir as following layout, this is the test run for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16904&quot; title=&quot;initial test script to run sanity.sh and sanityn.sh with PFL layout &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-16904&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-16904&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/53651/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/53651/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;compr_STRIPEPARAMS=&quot;-E 64k -c 1 -E 1M -c 2 -E eof -c 4 -S 4M&quot;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
